# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore — doa-ops-hub (Next.js 16)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Excluye de la build context todo lo que no necesita `next build`. Reduce
# tiempo de transfer al daemon y evita fugas de secretos o artefactos locales.
# =============================================================================

# --- VCS ---------------------------------------------------------------------
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# --- Dependencies (se instalan dentro de la imagen) --------------------------
node_modules
**/node_modules

# --- Next.js build outputs (se regeneran en la build) ------------------------
.next
out
.turbo
.swc
next-env.d.ts.bak

# --- Environments (NUNCA meter secretos en la imagen) ------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Logs / temporales -------------------------------------------------------
*.log
tmp-dev-err.log
tmp-dev-out.log
tmp
tmp/**

# --- Dev tools / IDE ---------------------------------------------------------
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Tests / coverage --------------------------------------------------------
coverage
.nyc_output
**/*.test.*
**/*.spec.*
__snapshots__
__tests__

# --- Docs / runbooks que no aportan a la imagen ------------------------------
README*.md
CHANGELOG.md
CLAUDE.md
docs
openspec
Formularios
"01. Soporte_App"

# --- Backends separados (el runner sólo es el frontend Next.js) --------------
# rag-backend es un proceso Python independiente — no entra en la imagen Next.
rag-backend

# --- Deploy / infra (no debe estar dentro del context de la app) -------------
# La carpeta "03. Deploy" vive fuera del app root, pero si alguien accidental-
# mente la copia dentro, la ignoramos explícitamente.
03.*Deploy
deploy.sh
docker-compose.yml
Dockerfile

# --- Salidas de scripts / procesado ------------------------------------------
scripts/output
scripts/*.log
tools/output

# --- Build cache de lightningcss / swc --------------------------------------
.cache
